NordicPlotter V1.0, Aug-2016
Saeed Soltani Moghadam, IIEES, Tehran, Iran
saeed.sltm@gmail.com

Note:

You can copy/distribut the code with your own responsibility.



Desription:

A simple python program to read a seisan nordic file
and plot event-station distribution with header
information if exist (focal mechanism plots).



Requires:

- Python
- Numpy
- Obspy
- SEISAN



Inputs:

- A nordic file (select.out)
- A station file (STATION0.HYP)



Outpus:

- fig directory for outpu figures.

Usage:

python NordicPlotter.py
